  <h1>Ember Charts</h1>
  <p class="elevated">A charting library built with the
  Ember.js and d3.js frameworks. It includes time series, bar, pie, and
  scatter charts which are easy to extend and modify. The out-of-the-box
  behavior these chart components represents our thoughts on best
  practices in chart interactivity and presentation.</p>
