      <h3>Features</h3>
      <ul class="styled">
        <li>Highly customizable and extensible.</li>
        <li>Rich with features - add legends, labels, tooltips, and
        mouseover effects.</li>
        <li>Robust & polished - weird data will not cause your charts to
        break.</li>
        <li>Roll your own charts by extending our ChartComponent class -
        get labels, automatic resizing, and reasonable defaults for
        margins, padding, etc.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
